<h2 id="Syntax" name="Syntax">Syntax</h2>
<pre class="twopartsyntaxbox"><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/Value_definition_syntax" title="CSS/Value_definition_syntax">Formal syntax</a>: <code><a href="/en-US/docs/CSS/integer" title="">&lt;integer&gt;</a></code>
</pre>
<pre>orphans: 2
orphans: 3

orphans: inherit
</pre>
<h3 id="Values" name="Values">Values</h3>
<dl><dt>
  <code>&lt;integer&gt;</code></dt>
 <dd>
  Only positive values are allowed.</dd>
 <dt>
  <code>inherit</code></dt>
 <dd>
  Takes the same specified value as the property for the element's parent.</dd>
</dl>